originalText.text: Best doctor hands down. The staff was incredible and the doctor took her time to address my medical needs. She is highly recommended.

text.text: Best doctor hands down. The staff was incredible and the doctor took her time to address my medical needs. She is highly recommended.

originalText.text: Where do I began?This office upholds high levels of professional diplomacy, that is with regards to mannerism,  and confidentiality. The receptionist noticed that I was experiencing difficulty with the electronic system and quickly modified my appointment to the same day. The doctor is superb within her field making it that she can simplify complex language to easier terms for us non doctors to understand! Both her and her assistant are females so they understand the challenges and/or discomfort that we as females might face during an examination. Thus the visit does not feel like a doctors visit, instead it feels like a regular conversation. I observed the doctor call the pharmacy to ensure that any medication being prescribed was there. Definitely would visit again. I went in as a client and gained a family! Phenomenal doctor and visit at large!

originalText.text: I am a patient at this clinic and I loved my experience with Dr. Anyichie. Extremely nice and very professional. I highly recommend her as a top provider in the area. The staff is just as great too.

originalText.text: Dr. Anyichie is very knowledgeable and caring. Wait time can be a little long in the Inwood office but then I always get her full attention. She's helped me navigate through two issues in the 8 years that I've been her patient. She looks at the full picture, not just the symptoms. I highly recommend her. The office staff is very caring as well, they've always helped me navigate my prescriptions and insurance.

I do not recommend doctor Anyichie.
